author: University of Arizona Athletics
title: Women's Tennis Set to Kick Off Spring Season at Home
text: Women's Tennis 01/16/2025 Arizona Athletics Women's Tennis Set to Kick Off Spring Season at Home TUCSON, Ariz.- The Wildcats are set to kick off their season this Friday at home in a doubleheader against Loyola Marymount at 10:00 a.m. MST and UCSD 2:00 p.m. MST. The last time Arizona faced off against Loyola Marymount Arizona fell 0-4 to the Lions in 2022. Arizona hosted UCSD for their Wildcat Invite in the Fall, and now they return for dual match. The last time the Cats faced off against the Tritons, Arizona defeated UCSD 4-0. On Monday, January 20th, the Cats will be back at LaNelle to host Cal Poly and Northern Arizona for another double header beginning at 10:00 a.m. MST. This weekends events will be streamed on PlaySight and live stats will be available on StatBroadcast. Print Friendly Version
